{
  "name": "Mind Blast",
  "type": "feature",
  "img": "icons/magic/lightning/orb-ball-purple.webp",
  "system": {
    "description": "<p>You can spend <strong>1 AP</strong> to psychically assault a creature's mind within 10 Spaces.</p><p>Make a <strong>Spell Check </strong>against the <strong>MD </strong>of a target within range.</p><p><strong>Hit: </strong>The target takes 1 Psychic damage.</p><p> </p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Action Point Enhancements</span></strong></span></p><p>You can choose to spend additional <strong>AP </strong>when you use this Feature, but before making the <strong>Spell Check</strong>. You can choose multiple effects or the same effect multiple times.</p><ul><li><strong>Damage: (1 AP)</strong> You deal +1 Psychic damage.</li><li><strong>Range: (1 AP)</strong> You increase the range by +5 Spaces. </li></ul><p>Choosing any of the following <strong>AP </strong>Enhancement options forces the target to make a <strong>Mental Save </strong>against the chosen effect. If you spend <strong>AP </strong>on multiple effects, the target only makes 1 Save against all effects.</p><ul><li><strong>Daze: (1 AP)</strong> The target becomes <strong>Dazed </strong>(DisADV on Mental Checks and Spell Checks) until the start of your next turn.</li><li><strong>Break Focus: (1 AP)</strong> The target loses their Concentration.</li><li><strong>Rend Mind: (1 AP)</strong> The target’s <strong>MD </strong>is reduced by 2 until the end of your next turn.</li><li><strong>Forceful: (1 AP) </strong>The target has DisADV on their Mental Save against this Feature.</li></ul><p> </p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Mana Point Enhancement</span></strong></span></p><p>You can spend 1 or more MP (up to your Combat Mastery) before you make the Spell Check to choose 2 additional AP Enhancements.</p>",
